<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Frankfurt am Main</head><p>Der Rat übersendet in Abschrift Neuigkeiten über König Sigismund und die Geschehnisse in Böhmen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_350" id="174r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_350_r1l14">Den von Frankfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_350_r1l15"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ʒu </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l16">etwas <expan>ʒuverſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> von gelegenheıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc künıgs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l17">vnd auch von den lewffen ʒu Beheim etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l18">vnd haben das in gut <expan>vercʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> wan wır deſmals nıht <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l19">meͣre dauon weſten . Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu wıſſen . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l21">ſeıd . einem bey vns / <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> ıſt ein ſchrıft von 
<add><ab facs="#facs_350_r1l20">gelegenheıt </ab></add> deſſelben <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedi </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l22">gıſten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>R<ex>ömiſchen</ex></expan> etc künıgs vnd auch der lewfft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l23">Beheım <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſchrıft er vns geweıſet hat . / der wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l24"><expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> verſloſſen <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l25"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_350" id="174r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Frankfurt</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> etwas <expan>zu
                            verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> von gelegenheit
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.
                        künigs und auch von den lewffen zu Beheim etc., das haben wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und haben das in gut
                                <expan>verczog<ex>en</ex></expan>, wan wir desmals niht
                                <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre davon westen. Also tun
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu wissen, daz seid einem bey uns
                                <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> ist ein schrift von
                            <add>gelegenheit</add> desselben <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedi
                        gisten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>r<ex>ömischen</ex></expan>
                        etc. künigs und auch der lewfft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Beheim,
                                <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> schrift er uns geweiset hat, der wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan> verslossen
                        <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
